sequenceDiagram
    participant OrderService
    participant EventBus
    participant PaymentService
    participant InventoryService
    participant NotificationService
    
    OrderService->>EventBus: OrderCreated Event
    EventBus->>PaymentService: OrderCreated
    PaymentService->>EventBus: PaymentProcessed Event
    
    EventBus->>InventoryService: PaymentProcessed
    InventoryService->>EventBus: ItemsReserved Event
    
    EventBus->>NotificationService: ItemsReserved
    NotificationService->>EventBus: CustomerNotified Event
    
    Note over EventBus: Each service listens<br/>and publishes events<br/>No central orchestrator